#### 6. Marionette Testing ⚠️ MANDATORY
**CRITICAL**: You MUST test all changes in the running app before opening a PR.

**Steps:**
1. Launch Flutter app: `flutter run -d macos > /tmp/flutter_run.log 2>&1 &`
